@UPLB Creepy Moment:

It happened during one of the nights when I was applying for an org. After our meeting in the main library, everyone went their separate ways--two of my batchmates(during the application) took the path to the closest bridge(I think it was the rumored "Never-Ending" Bridge?). My mind's kinda fuzzy about what I said back then... But as soon as I said the phrase, one of the lights flicked off, scaring my groupmates.

The fact that the place is "haunted", or I'm really a... magnet of misfortune.
